{"tid":637664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海關旺角先達掃場 數十手機店拉閘停業","createTime":"2018-04-22T04:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T09:20:10.000Z","uid":13474,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"36ceb000a0008b0193c6d94a89b5c072fcfc22e8","tid":637664,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T04:34:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180421&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58102295  海關旺角先達掃場 數十手機店拉閘停業\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180421%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58102295%20%20%E6%B5%B7%E9%97%9C%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E5%85%88%E9%81%94%E6%8E%83%E5%A0%B4%20%E6%95%B8%E5%8D%81%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E5%BA%97%E6%8B%89%E9%96%98%E5%81%9C%E6%A5%AD&d=1TjRAgKfIFbsuTug5DMmHTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=80fe3994\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180421%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D58102295%20%20%E6%B5%B7%E9%97%9C%E6%97%BA%E8%A7%92%E5%85%88%E9%81%94%E6%8E%83%E5%A0%B4%20%E6%95%B8%E5%8D%81%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E5%BA%97%E6%8B%89%E9%96%98%E5%81%9C%E6%A5%AD&h=8f7f5c04\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180421&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=58102295  海關旺角先達掃場 數十手機店拉閘停業</a><br />\n下午4時許，海關突擊搜查專門售賣手機及數碼影音產品的旺角先達廣場，現場消息稱，當時有數十海關人員到場，行動主要針對商場內有店舖疑違法聘用黑工及售賣冒牌手機配件等。受事件影響，有數十間手機店臨時拉閘暫停營業。<br />\n<br />\n據讀者提供的一條片段，當時有多名佩戴委任證的海關人員去到部份手機店調查，現場氣氛緊張，片段中可見有部份手機店在事發時關門拉閘，但仍有其他店舖繼續開門營業，並有市民如常到來選購手機。<br />\n<br />\n先達狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6317bb7d556ff03c21aa4eeb57bc46576f05038c","tid":637664,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T04:48:35.000Z","msg":"黑道糾紛？"},{"pid":"df8ea304922681fcf14242a23ecc440d6b8a946a","tid":637664,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T04:56:10.000Z","msg":"有水貨所以怕海關？ 因為忌水<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff1a8657f88895bb61056c3bcd566046cbc3968","tid":637664,"uid":80153,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T05:36:46.000Z","msg":"一早應該掃啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a955ffb4125522cf146fb0baa0a7e4e4d21b73e5","tid":637664,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:11:09.000Z","msg":"有幾多間無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c36d0b66512987e17d765bf905e344311e6751a","tid":637664,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:12:01.000Z","msg":"海關版權及商標調查科高級監督葉慧嬋透露，早前接獲舉報，於是突擊搜查12間店舖及2個單位，海關相信已成功搗破一個供應冒牌手機集團。行動中，海關亦發現，店舖涉嫌以不良營商手法欺騙消費者，以舊機充當新機，或以水貨假扮行貨出售。被捕人士包括男主腦及女骨幹成員。"},{"pid":"cfe5a44d87fe56969701238ca351c46122badc53","tid":637664,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T09:20:10.000Z","msg":"中興事件？"}]}